# User skill library

Global skills live in `~/.skills`. `pnpm run skills:link` (and template sync) symlinks each agent tree to that folder:

- `.cursor/skills` → `~/.skills`
- `.codex/skills` → `~/.skills`
- `.agent/skills` → `~/.skills`
- `.github/skills` → `~/.skills`

There is no repo-root `.skills` entry. The template keeps the **ui-ux-pro-max** payload under `.template-reference/ui-ux-pro-max/` for sync and workflows; copy or link it into `~/.skills/ui-ux-pro-max` if you want it in your global library.

When work matches packaged guidance, read the relevant `SKILL.md` under `~/.skills/<skill-id>/` (or via the symlinks above) instead of guessing.
